1
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:25,520
What's wrong?

2
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:29,280
There are some things

3
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:32,420
I don't know if I should keep investigating.

4
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:37,360
Back then, in the police force,

5
00:01:37,440 --> 00:01:39,440
you were the biggest troublemaker.

6
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:42,039
Are there cases you're afraid to investigate?

7
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:44,140
Sometimes, being too persistent

8
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:47,220
can get the people around you killed.

9
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:50,610
But now you have us by your side.

10
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:53,490
As police officers,

11
00:01:53,880 --> 00:01:54,539
sacrifices

12
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,440
are inevitable.

13
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:04,680
Where did this come from?

14
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:05,880
Someone sent it to me.

15
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:08,280
Why would they send it to you?

16
00:02:09,759 --> 00:02:10,639
Tian Liang.

17
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:13,200
Why is he in this photo?

18
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:17,200
Is this a clue or a red herring?

19
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,200
So I don't know

20
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:20,000
if I should keep investigating.

21
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:24,120
After all, the last time we investigated Liu Weishan, everything...

22
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:24,920
What's wrong?

23
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:27,280
Nothing.

24
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:31,930
This Liu Weishan

25
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:34,600
is a shareholder of the biggest company in Tongjiang City,

26
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,720
Xincheng Group.

27
00:02:37,079 --> 00:02:38,410
The relationships here

28
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:39,840
are deeply intertwined.

29
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:42,240
If we are going to investigate,

30
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,440
we must do it quietly.

31
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:45,000
If I remember correctly,

32
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:46,720
Tongda Group and Xincheng Group

33
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:49,180
have been competitors these past few years.

34
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:52,380
I suspect this is a tragedy

35
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:54,930
caused by vicious economic competition.

36
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:56,170
Liu Weishan.

37
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:58,280
Ye Qiming.

38
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:04,020
Let's investigate together.

39
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,010
Boss.

40
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:08,170
Two police officers just came looking for me.

41
00:03:08,880 --> 00:03:09,940
What did they want?

42
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,000
About the photos.

43
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:22,800
How did the photos get out?

44
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:25,520
It seems like it was planned.

45
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:29,720
These photos won't cause much trouble.

46
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,760
The main issue is that evidence.

47
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:33,680
Now,

48
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:36,680
is it really in Ye Qiming's hands?

49
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:39,800
He has now completely

50
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,600
become our enemy.

51
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:43,840
Got it.

52
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:48,200
From now on, you are the legal representative of this company.

53
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:49,040
Work hard.

54
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,200
Okay.

55
00:03:50,440 --> 00:03:52,240
I definitely won't let you down.

56
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:55,960
Sis,

57
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:57,480
don't go.

58
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,960
I really like you.

59
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,400
You're just a kid.

60
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:04,080
What do you know about liking someone?

61
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,120
I really like you.

62
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,560
I really like you.

63
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,240
I know.

64
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:23,120
Let me give you a little reward first.

65
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:25,360
This kid is really easy to coax.

66
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:31,240
Remember to come to me when you need me.

67
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,770
I will definitely help you.

68
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:33,730
Good boy.

69
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:54,680
Qiming.

70
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,560
You don't know how hard it was

71
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:59,300
not seeing you these two days.

72
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:03,440
I apologize for my capriciousness.

73
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:08,060
I've thought a lot these two days.

74
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:10,290
As long as I'm in your heart,

75
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:13,330
I can stop caring about anything else.

76
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,760
But I care.

77
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:24,440
Hello.

78
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,680
Mr. Ye, something happened at the construction site.

79
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:28,140
Okay, I'll be right there.

80
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,010
What exactly happened?

81
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:56,320
The floor collapsed,

82
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,720
and several people fell.

83
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,480
Take them to the hospital! Call 120!

84
00:05:59,480 --> 00:05:59,960
Okay.

85
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:18,520
I'm at the hospital right now.

86
00:06:18,520 --> 00:06:20,120
Three workers were injured.

87
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:22,210
Keep an eye on Ye Qiming.

88
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,200
Got it.

89
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:29,640
This elevator lobby, it's here.

90
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:30,480
Excuse me.

91
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:31,280
Coming through.

92
00:06:31,280 --> 00:06:32,159
Excuse me.

93
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:33,400
Who is Ye Qiming?

94
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:37,080
I am.

95
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,000
We are from the Safety Supervision Bureau.

96
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:40,159
Someone reported that your

97
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:42,480
construction site used substandard steel and cement,

98
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,880
causing worker casualties.

99
00:06:43,880 --> 00:06:46,409
You are fully responsible for this accident.

100
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,960
We hope you can come back with us for investigation.

101
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:50,290
Okay, I will cooperate.

102
00:06:52,080 --> 00:06:52,680
Hold this.

103
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:55,890
We must investigate this thoroughly.

104
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:57,600
After you.

105
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:03,920
Your company is suspected of using

106
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,080
substandard steel materials.

107
00:07:05,080 --> 00:07:06,080
Did you know that?

108
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:07,640
I didn't know.

109
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,780
You signed for this material.

110
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:17,900
I signed it.

111
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:20,450
But I used qualified steel rebars.

112
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:22,520
The company on the contract doesn't even exist.

113
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:24,450
Where did you get the steel rebars?

114
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:27,000
Slow down.

115
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,450
Go straight.

116
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:31,060
Go straight. Go straight.

117
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:36,520
Here.

118
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:41,100
Sign the purchasing contract for steel rebars and cement.

119
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:42,800
Sign it.

120
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:44,920
Write it here.

121
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:46,840
Here.

122
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:47,500
Right here,

123
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:48,330
write it.

124
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,420
Old classmate.

125
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:01,060
You must help me with this.

126
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:02,320
Qiming was framed.

127
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:09,720
After all, we've been classmates for so many years.

128
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:11,850
You can't just ignore our friendship.

129
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,500
Besides, you know Qiming.

130
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:15,960
You know he's not that kind of person.

131
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:17,490
He wouldn't do such a thing.

132
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,300
As for this matter,

133
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:25,290
let's wait until the investigation results are out.

134
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:26,160
So you mean

135
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,760
you're not going to help?

136
00:08:59,000 --> 00:08:59,960
It's done.

137
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:02,040
Ye Qiming has been taken away.

138
00:09:02,040 --> 00:09:03,560
Two workers were seriously injured,

139
00:09:03,560 --> 00:09:04,290
and one died.

140
00:09:04,680 --> 00:09:05,320
This time,

141
00:09:05,800 --> 00:09:07,000
he's going to suffer.

142
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,360
He deserves it.

143
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:15,160
This is your best chance to bring Ye Qiming down.

144
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:18,920
By the way.

145
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,880
Ye Qiming has an old classmate

146
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:23,200
who is running for mayor.

147
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:24,760
He seems to want to push him up.

148
00:09:24,760 --> 00:09:26,420
But that guy is a bit stubborn.

149
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:29,400
Ye Qiming

150
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:32,240
has been heavily suppressed by me these years.

151
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:35,280
He needs someone like Jiang Tao by his side.

152
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,760
Even if he can't help him,

153
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,160
he won't help me.

154
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,280
To him,

155
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:41,880
this is the utmost fairness.

156
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:47,020
He still underestimates my godfather's power.

157
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:49,520
After all, we now hold

158
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:52,300
the most useful bargaining chip.

159
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,800
Leave this to me.

160
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:08,480
According to Liu Weishan's subordinates,

161
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:10,280
he is not in Tongjiang right now.

162
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:11,280
We don't have

163
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:13,340
any more crucial evidence right now.

164
00:10:13,680 --> 00:10:15,680
Not being able to summon him is a big problem.

165
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:17,740
His identity is indeed a bit special.

166
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:21,280
But if we can summon him,

167
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,900
we might really be close to the truth.

168
00:10:25,160 --> 00:10:27,600
After all, all the evidence points to him now.

169
00:10:27,600 --> 00:10:28,640
Find a way.

170
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:34,160
How can we find this crucial evidence?

171
00:10:41,160 --> 00:10:43,400
How can we find this crucial evidence?

172
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,160
Should we let Xiao...

173
00:10:48,680 --> 00:10:49,480
What's wrong?

174
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:54,180
I need to go out.

175
00:10:58,880 --> 00:11:00,010
Where are you going?

176
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:07,940
Something came up at home.

177
00:11:10,680 --> 00:11:11,160
Shen...

178
00:11:33,880 --> 00:11:34,810
I have Song Qing.

179
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,000
Don't cross the line.

180
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:38,200
Or you will implicate those around you.

181
00:11:38,280 --> 00:11:39,940
Do you know what you did wrong?

182
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,570
I did nothing wrong.

183
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:45,220
What's wrong with investigating a case?

184
00:11:45,640 --> 00:11:46,880
Lao Wu, calm down.

185
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:48,720
I know about this,

186
00:11:48,880 --> 00:11:51,010
and we can't entirely blame Shen Feng.

187
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:52,760
After you received the call,

188
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:55,760
you should have reported to the bureau immediately.

189
00:11:55,760 --> 00:11:58,890
Then you wouldn't have missed Song Qing's text message.

190
00:12:00,920 --> 00:12:01,780
You need to know

191
00:12:01,880 --> 00:12:04,210
that Chief Wu and I have high hopes for you.

192
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:05,520
If you are this impulsive,

193
00:12:05,520 --> 00:12:06,920
how can you handle cases?

194
00:12:09,920 --> 00:12:11,120
It really is my fault.

195
00:12:12,920 --> 00:12:13,760
I'm sorry.

196
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:18,740
If I had seen the text message,

197
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:22,260
she wouldn't have been in danger.

198
00:12:24,560 --> 00:12:25,690
Where you went wrong

199
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,620
is being too arrogant,

200
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:28,980
acting alone too much,

201
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:31,180
and playing the lone hero.

202
00:12:31,680 --> 00:12:32,540
You should know

203
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:36,730
you have teammates around you that you can trust.

204
00:12:36,880 --> 00:12:38,340
In the police department,

205
00:12:39,280 --> 00:12:41,320
you are not the only one working.

206
00:12:43,160 --> 00:12:43,760
Chief,

207
00:12:44,520 --> 00:12:45,850
give me one more chance.

208
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:49,540
If I can't catch the killer, I'll take off this uniform myself.

209
00:12:57,160 --> 00:12:57,600
Here.

210
00:12:57,760 --> 00:12:59,040
You write the report now,

211
00:12:59,040 --> 00:13:00,520
and I'll approve it immediately.

212
00:13:00,520 --> 00:13:02,640
I think all your years at the police academy

213
00:13:02,640 --> 00:13:03,720
were a waste.

214
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:06,400
Three generations of your family have been in the police.

215
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:07,360
This uniform

216
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,560
is your family's honor.

217
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:15,360
The organization's disciplinary decision regarding you

218
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,280
has already been made.

219
00:13:16,280 --> 00:13:18,080
You are temporarily suspended from your post.

220
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:20,200
But we already have a lead on this case.

221
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:22,520
Can a decision made by the Provincial Department

222
00:13:22,520 --> 00:13:23,760
be revoked by me and the commissar

223
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:25,080
just because we say so?

224
00:13:25,720 --> 00:13:28,200
I think you should go back and re-educate yourself.

225
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:30,260
Learn how to be a proper person first.

226
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:53,560
Don't worry.

227
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:56,200
I won't ask anything.

228
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:59,570
I just want to stay with you for a while.

229
00:14:00,760 --> 00:14:01,680
Do you remember

230
00:14:04,560 --> 00:14:05,560
I told you?

231
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:09,730
It's not that I don't trust you.

232
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:14,340
I just don't dare to trust anyone.

233
00:14:17,160 --> 00:14:19,220
Actually, it's not about not daring.

234
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:25,440
I can't implicate anyone else anymore.

235
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:32,840
No.

236
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:34,600
Oh my god. How old are you?

237
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:36,460
Why are you acting like an old man?

238
00:14:46,280 --> 00:14:48,280
Do you know why I left the frontline?

239
00:14:56,440 --> 00:14:57,080
Why?

240
00:15:02,520 --> 00:15:04,240
Someone very important to me

241
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:10,000
was killed because of me.

242
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:18,600
Alright.

243
00:15:19,280 --> 00:15:20,540
Do you want some water?

244
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:22,560
I'll go get it for you.

245
00:15:22,560 --> 00:15:23,040
Okay.

246
00:15:33,040 --> 00:15:33,440
Hello,

247
00:15:33,800 --> 00:15:35,530
buddy. Can I ask you something?

248
00:15:35,920 --> 00:15:36,840
Is the steel procurement here

249
00:15:36,840 --> 00:15:38,000
all handled by Manager Chen?

250
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:38,840
Yes.

251
00:15:39,680 --> 00:15:41,540
When did you last purchase rebar?

252
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:44,080
I think it was July 25th.

253
00:15:44,280 --> 00:15:44,760
Where?

254
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:46,760
Near Daheishan, at a

255
00:15:46,920 --> 00:15:48,650
large steel wholesale market.

256
00:15:48,920 --> 00:15:50,560
By the way, is Manager Chen here?

257
00:15:50,560 --> 00:15:52,760
I haven't seen him for the past two days.

258
00:15:52,880 --> 00:15:53,880
All right, I'll leave you to it.

259
00:15:53,880 --> 00:15:54,560
Thank you.

260
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:55,160
Thanks.

261
00:15:58,840 --> 00:15:59,720
July 25th.

262
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:01,040
Dahei Mountain.
